# Product Service

This service manages the product catalog, including CRUD operations and price versioning. It exposes REST APIs as defined in the domain architecture.

## API Endpoints
- POST /api/v1/products
- GET /api/v1/products/{id}

## Tech Stack
- Java, Spring Boot
- Maven
- H2/PostgreSQL (configurable)
- Flyway for DB migrations

## Running Locally
```
mvn spring-boot:run
```

## Testing
```
mvn test
```

## Deployment
- Build Docker image: `docker build -t product-service .`
- Run: `docker run -p 8080:8080 product-service`

